  "datePublished": "2016-07-04T19:28:25-04:00",
  "dateModified": "2016-07-07T22:31:20-04:00",
  "description": "Sticky, sweaty, and occasionally stinky—getting a good night’s sleep when you're over-heated can be tough. Here are some tried and true ways to stay chill all night long. ",
  "about": [
    {
      "@type": "Thing",
      "name": "Grow",
      "sameAs": "http://greatist.com/grow"
    },
